name: ekd.crm.case.section
src: The code of the section must be unique !

name: ekd.crm.case.section
src: You can not create recursive accounts!
value: Вы не можете создать взаимозависимые счета!

name: ekd.crm.case.rule,act_email_cc
src: These people will receive a copy of the futur communication between party and users by email

name: ekd.crm.case.rule,act_remind_attach
src: Check this if you want that all documents attached to the case be attached to the reminder email sent.

name: ekd.crm.case.rule,act_remind_party
src: Check this if you want the rule to send a reminder by email to the party.

name: ekd.crm.case.rule,act_remind_user
src: Check this if you want the rule to send a reminder by email to the user.

name: ekd.crm.case.section,allow_unlink
src: Allows to delete non draft cases

name: ekd.crm.case.section,reply_to
src: The email address put in the 'Reply-To' of all emails sent by Open ERP about cases in this section

name: ekd.crm.segmentation,categ
src: The party category that will be added to partys that match the segmentation criterions after computation.

name: ekd.crm.segmentation,categ_id
src: The party category that will be added to partys that match the segmentation criterions after computation.

name: ekd.crm.segmentation,exclusif
src: Check if the category is limited to partys that match the segmentation criterions. If checked, remove the category from partys that doesn't match segmentation criterions

name: ekd.crm.segmentation,sales_purchase_active
src: Check if you want to use this tab as part of the segmentation rule. If not checked, the criteria beneath will be ignored

name: ekd.crm.segmentation,som_interval
src: A period is the average number of days between two cycle of sale or purchase for this segmentation. It's mainly used to detect if a party has not purchased or buy for a too long time, so we suppose that his state of mind has decreased because he probably bought goods to another supplier. Use this functionality for recurring businesses.

name: ekd.crm.segmentation,som_interval_decrease
src: If the party has not purchased (or bought) during a period, decrease the state of mind by this factor. It's a multiplication

name: ekd.crm.segmentation,som_interval_default
src: Default state of mind for period preceeding the 'Max Interval' computation. This is the starting state of mind by default if the party has no event.

name: ekd.crm.segmentation,som_interval_max
src: The computation is made on all events that occured during this interval, the past X periods.

name: ekd.crm.case.rule
src: E-Mail Reminders (includes the content of the case)

name: ekd.crm.case.rule
src: Special Keywords to Be Used in The Body
value: Специальные ключевые слова, могут быть использованы в письме

name: ekd.crm.case.rule
src: The rule use a AND operator. The case must match all non empty fields so that the rule execute the action described in the 'Actions' tab.

name: ekd.crm.case.section
src: Complete this if you use the mail gateway.
